<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="419760" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">重复同样的错误，觉得自身有不可克服的弱点。


</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
