<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户，<strong title="一只在找壳的蜗牛。" class="zu-question-my-bio">一只在找壳的蜗牛。</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="29">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$hy-zheng-36" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/hy-zheng-36" class="zg-link" title="hy zheng">hy zheng</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$max-rocky" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/max-rocky" class="zg-link" title="max rocky">max rocky</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="419760" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">我曾经错误地认为某个时刻是我最痛苦的时刻，结果后来一次次地被推翻……<br>现在我明白了，永远会有更痛苦的时刻出现，承受苦难的阈值是一直在提高的，<br>再也不用因为这是前所未有的痛苦，而感到恐惧绝望了。


</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
